---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Manifesto - BonsAI">
    <!-- Header with navigation -->
    <header class="bg-rice-paper border-b-2 border-charcoal-ink sticky top-0 z-50">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
            <a href="/" class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-charcoal-ink hover:text-olive-growth transition-colors">
                BonsAI
            </a>
            <a href="/" class="font-mono text-sm text-charcoal-ink/60 hover:text-charcoal-ink transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
                <span>← Back to Home</span>
            </a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <main class="bg-rice-paper min-h-screen py-20 px-4">
        <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <!-- Header -->
            <header class="mb-16 text-center border-b-2 border-charcoal-ink pb-10">
                <h1 class="font-heading font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl text-charcoal-ink mb-6">
                    Privacy Manifesto
                </h1>
                <p class="font-mono text-sm text-charcoal-ink/60">
                    Our commitment to user sovereignty and data ownership
                </p>
            </header>

            <!-- ========================================
                 REPLACE THE CONTENT BELOW WITH YOUR ACTUAL MANIFESTO
                 ======================================== -->
            
            <div class="space-y-12">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <h2 class="font-heading font-black text-4xl text-charcoal-ink">The BonsAI Protocol</h2>
                    <div class="font-heading text-2xl text-terracotta italic">Total Sovereignty</div>
                    <p class="mt-6 font-body text-lg text-charcoal-ink/80 leading-relaxed">
                        Privacy isn't a policy update; it's a compilation target. We built BonsAI with a single, uncompromising axiom: <strong class="text-charcoal-ink">Your data belongs to your hardware.</strong>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-charcoal-ink">I. Local-First, Local-Only</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-charcoal-ink/80 leading-relaxed">BonsAI is not a thin client for a cloud API. It is a self-contained intelligence engine.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-charcoal-ink/90">
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Inference on Your Metal:</strong> Every token is generated by your CPU/GPU.</span></li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Zero API Calls:</strong> Your prompts never leave your local network.</span></li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Offline by Default:</strong> Unplug the ethernet. Turn off the Wi-Fi. BonsAI works exactly the same.</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-charcoal-ink">II. The "Black Box" Guarantee</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-charcoal-ink/80 leading-relaxed">We cannot sell your data because we literally cannot see it.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-charcoal-ink/90">
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>No Training:</strong> We do not use your chats to train our models.</span></li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>No Telemetry:</strong> We don't track your keystrokes, your sentiment, or your usage hours.</span></li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>No Shadow Logs:</strong> What you type in BonsAI exists only in your local memory and vanishes when you clear it.</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="space-y-4">
                    <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-charcoal-ink">III. You Are Not the Product</h3>
                    <p class="font-body text-charcoal-ink/80 leading-relaxed">In an era of rent-seeking software, BonsAI is a tool you own.</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 font-body text-charcoal-ink/90">
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>No Account Required:</strong> No login walls. No email harvesting.</span></li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-olive-growth font-bold">•</span><span><strong>Your Keys, Your Castle:</strong> You control the encryption, the storage, and the deletion.</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                
            </div>

            <!-- ========================================
                 END OF FILLER CONTENT - REPLACE ABOVE
                 ======================================== -->

            <!-- Call to action -->
            <div class="mt-20 pt-12 border-t-2 border-charcoal-ink text-center">
                <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-olive-growth text-rice-paper font-heading font-bold text-xl px-10 py-4 border-2 border-charcoal-ink shadow-base hover:translate-x-[2px] hover:translate-y-[2px] hover:shadow-none transition-all">
                    Try BonsAI
                </a>
            </div>
        </article>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
